  30 May 2016; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Remove use of the deprecated games eclass

  30 May 2016; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Fix Blender addon install location

  16 May 2016; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Remove unused cmake variable

  16 May 2016; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Use pre-built data files

  29 Nov 2015; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Added CURL to crash reporter dependencies

  16 Aug 2015; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Update required GLM version

  16 Aug 2015; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Enable C++11 mode by default

  16 Aug 2015; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Sync with changes from main portage tree

  06 Jun 2014; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Added missing GLM dependency.

  06 Jun 2014; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Updated static linking dependencies: FreeType and ZLIB can now be statically
  linked.

  06 Nov 2013; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Add support for media-libs/libsdl2.
  Also import changes from main tree and update to git-r3.

  30 Jun 2013; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Make use of new features and dependency changes in the upcoming 1.1 release

  30 Jun 2013; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Import changes from in-tree ebuild

  08 Mar 2013; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Add slot to media-libs/libsdl dependency

  03 Mar 2013; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Move Qt dependencies to the new category

  01 Aug 2012; Daniel Scharrer <dscharrer@gentoo.org>
  -arx-libertatis-1.0.ebuild, -arx-libertatis-1.0.1.ebuild,
  -arx-libertatis-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Remove obsolete ebuilds so people will get the newer ones from the tree

  01 Aug 2012; Daniel Scharrer <dscharrer@gentoo.org>
  arx-libertatis-9999.ebuild:
  Update the live ebuild with the changes from the latest non-live ebuild in
  the tree

*arx-libertatis-1.0.2 (14 Jun 2012)

  14 Jun 2012; Daniel Scharrer <dscharrer@gentoo.org>
  arx-libertatis-1.0.1.ebuild, +arx-libertatis-1.0.2.ebuild:
  Bump version to 1.0.2

  22 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-1.0.ebuild, arx-libertatis-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Add amd64 and x86 keywords

*arx-libertatis-1.0.1 (22 Apr 2012)

  22 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-1.0.ebuild, +arx-libertatis-1.0.1.ebuild:
  Bump version to 1.0.1
  - Fixed garbled text rendering in the Russian version (upstream bug #226)
  - Fixed a crash in the critical error dialog on some Tux.png Linux systems
  (upstream crash report #229)
  - Loading files from the 'graph' and 'misc' directories is now
  case-insensitive

  22 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-1.0.ebuild:
  Add sourceforge mirror for version 1.0.

  19 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
  arx-libertatis-1.0.ebuild:
  Keyword amd64 x86

*arx-libertatis-1.0 (19 Apr 2012)

  19 Apr 2012; Daniel Scharrer <daniel@constexpr.org>
